1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,800
Falcons somehow one step ahead.
猎鹰不知怎么又提前一步。

2
00:00:01,800 --> 00:00:05,066
All the staging, all the signs pointed towards the A play.
前面的铺垫和信号，全都像是在指向 A 点。

3
00:00:05,866 --> 00:00:08,400
karrigan had his pieces in the right place.
大表哥 也早就把人摆在了正确位置。

4
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:12,433
It's now a chance at another OT.
现在又有机会拖进加时。

5
00:00:16,266 --> 00:00:20,033
Falcons had two chances in regulation they couldn't close.
猎鹰 在常规时间里有两次结束比赛的机会，但都没能把握住。

6
00:00:20,033 --> 00:00:23,866
This is FURIA's second chance all the same.
而 黑豹 这边，同样迎来了第二次机会。

7
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:37,433
They play it together.
他们聚在一起

8
00:00:37,466 --> 00:00:42,966
KSCERATO in lobby. FURIA walk outside.
KSCERATO 留在黄房，FURIA 这边往外场走。

9
00:00:47,166 --> 00:00:49,300
This is a fight between m0NESY and molodoy.
这一波，像是 m0NESY 和 molodoy 的正面对决。

10
00:00:49,300 --> 00:00:52,500
We might get to see it in round 30.
第 30 回合，真可能就在这里见分晓。

11
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:59,466
The damage done on YEKINDAR.
YEKINDAR 先被打出伤害。

12
00:00:59,466 --> 00:01:02,600
That's your aggressive lurker brought down so low.
这个负责前顶和单摸的人，血量已经被压得很低了。

13
00:01:04,066 --> 00:01:06,600
They just want this fight. They just want this pick.
他们就是想强行接这波枪，想先抓一个。

14
00:01:06,833 --> 00:01:08,300
m0NESY's not giving it.
但 m0NESY 不给这个机会。

15
00:01:09,566 --> 00:01:13,966
Oh, NiKo nearly punished. Will get gun on in time.
NiKo 差一点被逮到机，不过Niko还是架住了枪。

16
00:01:14,833 --> 00:01:18,300
YEKINDAR cleaned up. The early advantage going the way of Falcons.
YEKINDAR 被收掉，前期优势已经倒向 Falcons。

17
00:01:19,266 --> 00:01:24,100
Almost made it down, but so has kyousuke.
差一点就能下到下层，但 kyousuke 也已经同步跟到了。

18
00:01:25,266 --> 00:01:28,433
The yard hit has to come now.
外场这波必须现在就打了。

19
00:01:28,433 --> 00:01:33,100
FalleN wrestling back a kill here on this main lurk.
FalleN 在正门单摸这边，硬是扳回了一个人头。

20
00:01:33,266 --> 00:01:35,233
Clashing with his captain counterpart.
他对上的，正是另一边的指挥位。

21
00:01:35,500 --> 00:01:37,933
Bomb still being played forward into lower.
炸弹这边，还是在往下层推进。

22
00:01:38,866 --> 00:01:43,133
molodoy's been spotted. It's the info on the early rotate out of kyousuke.
molodoy 已经被看到了，这条信息也让 kyousuke 提前开始转点。

23
00:01:43,133 --> 00:01:44,566
They're gonna try and end this upper.
他们想直接从上层把这回合结束掉。

24
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:46,566
FalleN right now is taking space away in heaven.
而 FalleN 这会儿还在天堂位继续抢空间。

25
00:01:46,566 --> 00:01:49,800
This is a crazy move. This is a wild call.
这波动作太疯狂了，这个决策也太大胆了。

26
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:55,400
It all hinges on KSCERATO and FalleN at this top site.
上层这边，胜负现在几乎就压在 KSCERATO 和 FalleN 身上。

27
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:58,066
TeSeS has the info, sees them in the vents.
TeSeS 已经拿到信息了，也看到了通风管里的人。

28
00:01:58,466 --> 00:02:00,933
Can guess what's coming his way.
他已经能猜到接下来要发生什么。

29
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:03,533
KSCERATO shuts him down.
KSCERATO 直接把他打掉。

30
00:02:03,533 --> 00:02:06,600
And that top site cracked wide open.
上层防线一下就被撕开了。

31
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:10,333
Falcons have had some miraculous rounds,
Falcons 前面已经打出过几次神奇回合了，

32
00:02:10,333 --> 00:02:14,133
but right now kyousuke and m0NESY have got to summon something else.
但现在，kyousuke 和 m0NESY 还得再拿出点更夸张的东西。

33
00:02:16,166 --> 00:02:18,366
First kill goes m0NESY's way.
m0NESY先拿下第一个人头

34
00:02:19,900 --> 00:02:22,400
Hands off the keyboard. No one move a muscle.
现在谁都别乱动，手都先离开键盘。

35
00:02:22,466 --> 00:02:23,966
Time will do the heavy lifting.
接下来，时间会替他们做大部分工作。

36
00:02:23,966 --> 00:02:26,166
Time will solve this for us.
时间会替他们把问题解决掉。

37
00:02:26,533 --> 00:02:30,133
Time is all we need. How many times have we heard that?
他们现在最需要的就是时间。这话我们都听过多少次了。

38
00:02:34,533 --> 00:02:39,300
kyousuke looking for that first incision.
kyousuke 在找第一个突破口。

39
00:02:39,733 --> 00:02:41,600
Finds yuurih back at the site.
他先在包点后方逮到了 yuurih。

40
00:02:42,133 --> 00:02:44,300
Brazilians getting picked apart.
黑豹正在被逐个击破。

41
00:02:44,300 --> 00:02:48,266
And it ends up with this: m0NESY top performer.
最后就打成了这样，m0NESY 成了全场最关键的人。

42
00:02:48,266 --> 00:02:52,666
FalleN dead. The captain brushed aside.
FalleN 倒下，指挥被直接清掉。

43
00:02:52,966 --> 00:02:57,300
A nail-biter of a defuse that just comes in.
最后这个拆包，惊险到了极点。

44
00:02:58,700 --> 00:03:01,700
m0NESY is magic.
孩神神了！

